    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 24 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 20 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>As a reaction when you would take non-psychic damage , you spend the CCD Drain of this enhancement to create a ring of earth around your body by forcing the ground to raise. </p><p>You create a circular barrier of earth that has 7d10 hit points and resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage. </p><p>The barrier lasts until it reaches 0 hit points or until the start of your next turn.</p>",
